{"tid":2374261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"比亞迪配股集資298億　分析料視市況決定是否再集資","createTime":"2021-01-21T05:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T07:21:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7285e479684d7c6ebd1b006a4127ad9c7793e74","tid":2374261,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571571-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571571-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=e38ae5bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571571-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fc74304f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571571-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n比亞迪公布配股計劃，集資淨額約298億元。公司以每股225元配售1.33億股H股，相當於經擴大已發行H股數目約12.69%，每股配售價較昨日收市價折讓約7.8%。<br />\n<br />\n星展認為，比亞迪早已公布配股消息，現時落實計劃，市場並不感到意外，而且公司受晶片短缺的影響較小，股價有望繼續向上。<br />\n<br />\n不過，中證監批准公司在1年內，發行最多1.83億股H股，相當於現有H股股本約20%。而今次配股只佔獲批額度的66%，市場關注比亞迪何時再次配股。<br />\n<br />\n招銀國際研究部策略師蘇沛豐說，配股攤薄每股盈利，但只要資金能夠提升產能及研發投入，市場仍然憧憬盈利前景。他相信，比亞迪會視乎市況再決定是否集資，股價波幅將會加劇，但相信行業前景不變。<br />\n<br />\n今個月已有多家上市公司配股集資，包括藥明生物、康方生物、東方教育。蘇沛豐相信，會有更多公司趁市況良好配股集資，風電、太陽能及汽車等資本密集行業風險較高，但市場反應會較分歧，要視乎集資後的發展計劃。"},{"pid":"09706bb05259061e42ca1f8ab6cf3f9bc777c442","tid":2374261,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"炒高抽水散貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a6e39595efb47023918437757f0122905e9956","tid":2374261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"股災<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb54b930955d363be6bfd84146e60d16c24fe9f","tid":2374261,"uid":292108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:10:11.000Z","msg":"一早見到個咁既消息都升到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識玩"},{"pid":"c0674800a3b15e98c67934e1c13a35b6a1d6fe3d","tid":2374261,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb54b930955d363be6bfd84146e60d16c24fe9f","tid":2374261,"uid":292108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:10:11.000Z","msg":"一早見到個咁既消息都升到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"無得玩，佢唔係一般配股<br />\n<br />\n正常配股跌完先升，而家就抽高散水"}]}